{"tid":284291,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"外匯投資你問我答","createTime":"2017-06-14T19:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-05T19:03:30.000Z","uid":117333,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ffdbc391ab04a32f7c2f78ebcacc6622bcec6e73","tid":284291,"uid":117333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T19:40:34.000Z","msg":"玩左外匯保證金3年<br />\n第一年邊虧邊學<br />\n到第二年開始由虧轉盈<br />\n<br />\n如果有咩問題答到既都會盡答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e88587e1f4cdd5d3bb6836426560fec948540acc","tid":284291,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T19:43:36.000Z","msg":"最近美元升定跌？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n通常咩技術指標分析？"},{"pid":"e1838301843c5c86ded3b17115d2b27f394c5531","tid":284291,"uid":1706,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T19:45:23.000Z","msg":"總共賺左幾多？"},{"pid":"39e386f6682193029e92d1a859313084fe5ea17b","tid":284291,"uid":117333,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T19:52:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最近美元升定跌？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n通常咩技術指標分析？</blockquote><br />\n美元近期我覺得如果無咩大事,都係中性遍弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n主要用開壓力線,陰陽燭,MACD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522b096da1bb485ec0bbc0cb3fff107e9cf298e0","tid":284291,"uid":117333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T19:53:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>總共賺左幾多？</blockquote><br />\n細數目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d52cd954657df3e52eb9c8a649509798ed9aedd","tid":284291,"uid":67302,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T23:03:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>總共賺左幾多？</blockquote><br />\n細數目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講你就講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對誠仔黎講一百萬又係細數目<br />\n對我黎誠一蚊幾毫先係細數目<br />\n鬼知你講緊幾多錢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"338a1920a8122efb8896d6ebfd51860afe26758b","tid":284291,"uid":37631,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T23:12:26.000Z","msg":"係咩網/渠道睇新聞/新消息多？"},{"pid":"fb99e98f6949d4215de902d47e63681542494ea2","tid":284291,"uid":9446,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T23:13:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>總共賺左幾多？</blockquote><br />\n細數目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你老母 乜都唔講清楚開你問我答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a35037e86abb8c41bf446eeea2a2ce76e00624d","tid":284291,"uid":74368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T23:44:25.000Z","msg":"紐紙升定跌?"},{"pid":"159aa9d96a05d39e8f64d06b74c445f59416293c","tid":284291,"uid":54884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T03:20:46.000Z","msg":"次次打完我個止蝕就會反彈"},{"pid":"32100806bf425c488d06a54dd77be9f40dc9bdc8","tid":284291,"uid":4645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T04:04:19.000Z","msg":"通常幾耐開一個trade?<br />\n一個trade通常睇幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 ： 輸左三年 夾埋都幾十個"},{"pid":"6cbf67be4bf73b0c313ffad56aa2f792e0d5b923","tid":284291,"uid":69022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T04:09:07.000Z","msg":"爆過幾次倉？<br />\nleverage幾多？"},{"pid":"031ce4c4bc5befb3d3dbc1dccd3ae623f7cdb217","tid":284291,"uid":117333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T04:26:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咩網/渠道睇新聞/新消息多？</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://中文睇開大陸既fx168.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E7%9D%87%E9%96%8B%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E6%97%A2fx168.com&d=7zzUWbBCWXR1ISRxLjE2bIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=cf3fb2ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">中文睇開大陸既fx168.com</a>"},{"pid":"7e7712f8a7a1d787f7b1e12fb67c493b9890796c","tid":284291,"uid":117333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T04:29:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>紐紙升定跌?</blockquote><br />\n如果兌美元,紐紙仲係升勢入面"},{"pid":"d252aed564b5c6e4eb0360a1ac8db0b0f5d230ae","tid":284291,"uid":117333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T04:31:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>次次打完我個止蝕就會反彈</blockquote><br />\n巴打止損放得好近?<br />\n我就因為習慣分段入,所以唔會點放止損,就算放都可能成百點以上"},{"pid":"dfb28cb80f027c3224304d839747c2675885a0f1","tid":284291,"uid":49861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T04:39:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>紐紙升定跌?</blockquote><br />\n如果兌美元,紐紙仲係升勢入面</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/123919_d24ee0114b665f1f3c4dad2a7b0970f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2F123919_d24ee0114b665f1f3c4dad2a7b0970f0.jpg&h=38da5457&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7523fa8ee1abdabdf6eed9c1a94050df2855a718","tid":284291,"uid":117333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T04:41:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常幾耐開一個trade?<br />\n一個trade通常睇幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 ： 輸左三年 夾埋都幾十個</blockquote><br />\n幾耐Trade一次好難講,因為我都係睇指標做人<br />\n大概一個月有效既信號十幾次或以下<br />\n所以單量唔會多<br />\n我一次trade睇既時間長度,都係跟價格,<br />\n如果逆方向走我會加倉,如果順勢就一直拉止損鎖盈<br />\n所以無話一到時間就走人<br />\n硬要計既話上個月最長攞過一個星期"},{"pid":"640e234718f01472399f84fc89499f368d9e69aa","tid":284291,"uid":117333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T04:43:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爆過幾次倉？<br />\nleverage幾多？</blockquote><br />\n爆過一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5fd4ee02fd99fe23dea93ddc3b62de5b68a79f","tid":284291,"uid":117333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T04:43:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>紐紙升定跌?</blockquote><br />\n如果兌美元,紐紙仲係升勢入面</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/123919_d24ee0114b665f1f3c4dad2a7b0970f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2F123919_d24ee0114b665f1f3c4dad2a7b0970f0.jpg&h=38da5457&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打厲害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d19dcf3ca47f3e5febddadf2576b43a75b1518b","tid":284291,"uid":13514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T04:47:00.000Z","msg":"點睇日元???"},{"pid":"b40991ed81d10fb49033e06012209ed48b04a078","tid":284291,"uid":117333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T04:47:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>爆過幾次倉？<br />\nleverage幾多？</blockquote><br />\n爆過一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nleverage就1:200同1:500都有"},{"pid":"5dc84e395ea83ddfc6b4e21857d256a1367da0a5","tid":284291,"uid":117333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T04:52:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇日元???</blockquote><br />\n我既指標信號係中性,無明顯趨勢<br />\n不過純睇圖,直觀上兌美元,日元遍強狀態"},{"pid":"537a69139f19f1c67cee24a7554ad0c1a4b5e229","tid":284291,"uid":117333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T05:10:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>通常幾耐開一個trade?<br />\n一個trade通常睇幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 ： 輸左三年 夾埋都幾十個</blockquote><br />\n幾耐Trade一次好難講,因為我都係睇指標做人<br />\n大概一個月有效既信號十幾次或以下<br />\n所以單量唔會多<br />\n我一次trade睇既時間長度,都係跟價格,<br />\n如果逆方向走我會加倉,如果順勢就一直拉止損鎖盈<br />\n所以無話一到時間就走人<br />\n硬要計既話上個月最長攞過一個星期</blockquote><br />\n唔記得講因為只玩六個pair,所以量會遍少"},{"pid":"d2b7c789ab26ece43b1ef45261cc0f0e10a2c37a","tid":284291,"uid":4645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T05:29:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>通常幾耐開一個trade?<br />\n一個trade通常睇幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 ： 輸左三年 夾埋都幾十個</blockquote><br />\n幾耐Trade一次好難講,因為我都係睇指標做人<br />\n大概一個月有效既信號十幾次或以下<br />\n所以單量唔會多<br />\n我一次trade睇既時間長度,都係跟價格,<br />\n如果逆方向走我會加倉,如果順勢就一直拉止損鎖盈<br />\n所以無話一到時間就走人<br />\n硬要計既話上個月最長攞過一個星期</blockquote><br />\n唔記得講因為只玩六個pair,所以量會遍少</blockquote><br />\n指標自己睇？ 外匯一日都出10幾個指標 好易中伏.."},{"pid":"0b6fbe82fcf5fd0774ebac68724af725728d3ce8","tid":284291,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T06:23:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最近美元升定跌？<br />\n通常咩技術指標分析？</blockquote><br />\n美元近期我覺得如果無咩大事,都係中性遍弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n主要用開壓力線,陰陽燭,MACD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n解唔解釋到點解係加息週期美元跌?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMACD日圖似有反彈, 點睇?"},{"pid":"a1220b33b094f2a0ee5b18a579c55317cf33a728","tid":284291,"uid":117333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T11:02:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>通常幾耐開一個trade?<br />\n一個trade通常睇幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 ： 輸左三年 夾埋都幾十個</blockquote><br />\n幾耐Trade一次好難講,因為我都係睇指標做人<br />\n大概一個月有效既信號十幾次或以下<br />\n所以單量唔會多<br />\n我一次trade睇既時間長度,都係跟價格,<br />\n如果逆方向走我會加倉,如果順勢就一直拉止損鎖盈<br />\n所以無話一到時間就走人<br />\n硬要計既話上個月最長攞過一個星期</blockquote><br />\n唔記得講因為只玩六個pair,所以量會遍少</blockquote><br />\n指標自己睇？ 外匯一日都出10幾個指標 好易中伏..</blockquote><br />\n外匯得確咩指標都有得用<br />\n所以我用一個指標最基本要求係大概都要知佢原理,用咩計出黎<br />\n然後我用既趨勢指標都會幾個周期一齊睇做互相驗證<br />\n所以會較少中伏"},{"pid":"2c663b1f6b475c02eaba283bc5bb04c15b900fde","tid":284291,"uid":117333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T11:13:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>最近美元升定跌？<br />\n通常咩技術指標分析？</blockquote><br />\n美元近期我覺得如果無咩大事,都係中性遍弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n主要用開壓力線,陰陽燭,MACD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n解唔解釋到點解係加息週期美元跌?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMACD日圖似有反彈, 點睇?</blockquote><br />\n因為加息周期長,每次力道都唔大且合符市場預期,所以唔會話有咩大影響,反而美聯儲發表既言論比我感覺影響力仲大,就好似今日宣佈利率前因遍軟言論既一波走動<br />\n 日圓難講雖然各周期有一定既回調,但都未有特別既突破出現"},{"pid":"bac186d204d251b25a70abd55a581785f7bf8978","tid":284291,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T18:55:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>最近美元升定跌？<br />\n通常咩技術指標分析？</blockquote><br />\n美元近期我覺得如果無咩大事,都係中性遍弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n主要用開壓力線,陰陽燭,MACD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n解唔解釋到點解係加息週期美元跌?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMACD日圖似有反彈, 點睇?</blockquote><br />\n因為加息周期長,每次力道都唔大且合符市場預期,所以唔會話有咩大影響,反而美聯儲發表既言論比我感覺影響力仲大,就好似今日宣佈利率前因遍軟言論既一波走動<br />\n 日圓難講雖然各周期有一定既回調,但都未有特別既突破出現</blockquote><br />\n可能我1999左<br />\n美元日缐圖<br />\nAnyway 琴晚開始升左少少，你會估佢可以到咩位？"},{"pid":"f5dad3b0bfa833838ca68157158c9eb5c01582c2","tid":284291,"uid":46014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T19:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d0812cdcb01fe5e9904d09396de8a4a4ec09f6f","tid":284291,"uid":67141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T19:25:58.000Z","msg":"點解trade forex而唔係stock/futures/option"},{"pid":"fc9658a4611b8942d41eba54093b3812c7c92eaf","tid":284291,"uid":117333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T20:23:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>最近美元升定跌？<br />\n通常咩技術指標分析？</blockquote><br />\n美元近期我覺得如果無咩大事,都係中性遍弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n主要用開壓力線,陰陽燭,MACD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n解唔解釋到點解係加息週期美元跌?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMACD日圖似有反彈, 點睇?</blockquote><br />\n因為加息周期長,每次力道都唔大且合符市場預期,所以唔會話有咩大影響,反而美聯儲發表既言論比我感覺影響力仲大,就好似今日宣佈利率前因遍軟言論既一波走動<br />\n 日圓難講雖然各周期有一定既回調,但都未有特別既突破出現</blockquote><br />\n可能我1999左<br />\n美元日缐圖<br />\nAnyway 琴晚開始升左少少，你會估佢可以到咩位？</blockquote><br />\n如果升勢繼續可以睇111.780依個位置作短期目標,如果升破就睇114.370"},{"pid":"06d8cca6a080d466110118dfc41d0bd203c14333","tid":284291,"uid":117333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T20:29:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解trade forex而唔係stock/futures/option</blockquote><br />\n一開始主要係因為股票選股煩,而且無得沽空,所以有轉投資工具諗頭<br />\n然後就睇過下期貨,但即使細期都唔夠錢玩<br />\n後黎見到外匯入門唔洗好多錢就開始玩<br />\n玩落發現輔具工具(指標,EA......)隨手可得,唔似股票之類咁煩<br />\n所以就一直玩到依家"},{"pid":"5e80e8724df74cdcea73f840c806886d7c00335d","tid":284291,"uid":117333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T20:31:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42b4867d2ae8dbdf09e6c39aba9d3ca3f3610a54","tid":284291,"uid":121012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T20:34:56.000Z","msg":"點開始學投資?/有咩途徑"},{"pid":"33517f52165310337b135c5c6389f87252f3e5fd","tid":284291,"uid":117333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T20:40:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點開始學投資?/有咩途徑</blockquote><br />\n最實在既方法就係真槍實彈落場打同睇書"},{"pid":"343f094035151deb2740f3ffa26f38a9e3c325ae","tid":284291,"uid":117333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T20:42:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點開始學投資?/有咩途徑</blockquote><br />\n最實在既方法就係真槍實彈落場打同睇書</blockquote><br />\n對於會認輸知錯既人,爆倉係一個加速成長既方法"},{"pid":"14c630063afbc6898f2e817a85535768756bf9d1","tid":284291,"uid":121012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T20:44:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點開始學投資?/有咩途徑</blockquote><br />\n最實在既方法就係真槍實彈落場打同睇書</blockquote><br />\n有無新手書介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同埋一開始應該點入手/ 試邊類型?"},{"pid":"ce84ef4450579ec6b2f72f33f87016c9296d9a09","tid":284291,"uid":117333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T20:54:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點開始學投資?/有咩途徑</blockquote><br />\n最實在既方法就係真槍實彈落場打同睇書</blockquote><br />\n有無新手書介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同埋一開始應該點入手/ 試邊類型?</blockquote><br />\n通向財務自由之路<br />\n外匯市場技術分析<br />\n兩本都係會講有關心理,交易風格引導,交易系統,資金管理........<br />\n我覺得係唔錯既入門書,兩本網上都有得DL<br />\n然後睇既同時開個模擬帳戶習慣下點操作,防止犯低級錯誤(開錯方向,打錯手數...)<br />\n睇完兩本就入個一千幾百美直接打過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db6d0921835b7af0911587d98e7c6083c2b56535","tid":284291,"uid":121012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T21:27:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點開始學投資?/有咩途徑</blockquote><br />\n最實在既方法就係真槍實彈落場打同睇書</blockquote><br />\n有無新手書介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同埋一開始應該點入手/ 試邊類型?</blockquote><br />\n通向財務自由之路<br />\n外匯市場技術分析<br />\n兩本都係會講有關心理,交易風格引導,交易系統,資金管理........<br />\n我覺得係唔錯既入門書,兩本網上都有得DL<br />\n然後睇既同時開個模擬帳戶習慣下點操作,防止犯低級錯誤(開錯方向,打錯手數...)<br />\n睇完兩本就入個一千幾百美直接打過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n些些ching <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  !!!"},{"pid":"d520081300ef8ae49e134f922628e982cf993ed0","tid":284291,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T02:29:23.000Z","msg":"唔放止損放止賺會唔會好易輸多贏少??<br />\n用開咩網睇圖??"},{"pid":"30abe698ae6161a22c739e0adc73908de9284231","tid":284291,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T02:53:28.000Z","msg":"英鎊點睇？"},{"pid":"cd7724be23c8bcfbbda7b65218c2a7b069ca536f","tid":284291,"uid":53578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:25:21.000Z","msg":"點入門？"},{"pid":"e9f31ee124adc74f1a52e5feaff5fed3ae9aef6b","tid":284291,"uid":44798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:49:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5332228c20b1e9bd8efec72b01222960833a978f","tid":284291,"uid":81443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:56:09.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"b978505a702cf14ab9dee1795e47ba05845fd18a","tid":284291,"uid":100804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T12:17:40.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"846dd320c9bae0aab35a0dc4f6e424e17e9549f8","tid":284291,"uid":117333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T12:27:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔放止損放止賺會唔會好易輸多贏少??<br />\n用開咩網睇圖??</blockquote><br />\n如果唔放止損放止盈,出現既情況應該係贏多輸少<br />\n因為得盈利單會平倉,而且會出現一條幾靚既盈利增長線<br />\n不過一般情況都係假像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6514288b596e89aa41c7f6f0cb80a2a94b327f7d","tid":284291,"uid":117333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T12:30:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>英鎊點睇？</blockquote><br />\n英鎊兌美元雖然指標仲係未出,不