 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"334ab4218cc27b783794f8ea82dd971626c2faa3","tid":284291,"uid":103362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T14:55:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打用開咩平台做買賣，有冇教學？<br />\nThx</blockquote><br />\n用開icmarket,依個平台係外匯平台入面已經係唔錯既選擇<br />\n一黎ECN,二黎收費合理<br />\n然後巴打要咩教學?可唔可以明確D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nECN有咩好處，SPREAD細D？"},{"pid":"ad6dcdd24c3d452de7c389c49c0a20bb8a17db6e","tid":284291,"uid":117333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T15:44:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打用開咩平台做買賣，有冇教學？<br />\nThx</blockquote><br />\n用開icmarket,依個平台係外匯平台入面已經係唔錯既選擇<br />\n一黎ECN,二黎收費合理<br />\n然後巴打要咩教學?可唔可以明確D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nECN有咩好處，SPREAD細D？</blockquote><br />\nECN好處點差低,然後滑點既情況無咁多,就算出現滑點幅度都唔會太大<br />\n不過雖然點差低,但多左樣庫存費,所以長hold既話用forex同fxcm呢類浮動點差既交易成本會低D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d47e702ffdf322ee493b0d87dbf6bcafcd7f8f7","tid":284291,"uid":2833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:33:57.000Z","msg":"巴打玩開咩PAIR??"},{"pid":"c5395edba5b4725eb21ef3f880deaafb4b592bef","tid":284291,"uid":117333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T09:37:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打玩開咩PAIR??</blockquote><br />\n玩開USDCAD,USDJPY,GBPUSD,AUDUSD,EURUSD,USDCHF依六個直盤<br />\n不過依兩三個月波動都好似低左,所以最近加左GBPJPY落去試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d55a648ed49a5c29ed0e2b6f63c4cf92b21338","tid":284291,"uid":81340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T11:21:29.000Z","msg":"幾時可以玩到唔洗返工?"},{"pid":"579ea2c64b337d2ba53c659d692e3c33914dd443","tid":284291,"uid":117333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T11:39:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾時可以玩到