quote>其實外匯係咪要本大先搵到食？</blockquote><br />\n唔係因為有槓桿所以本唔需要太大都可以搵到食<br />\n而我自己哥套系統就十幾到廿萬,大概搵到月均一萬到兩萬<br />\n算係比較垃圾既系統</blockquote><br />\n咁你覺得有幾多本先好玩？</blockquote><br />\n我見入場低到幾十到二百美都有,不過我建議可以一千美入場,<br />\n然後低風險既可以玩0.01lot起手<br />\n中風險就0.1lot起手<br />\n之後順左再加錢</blockquote>"},{"pid":"89731a77b992b50288d17c44e5ee98c9531178b2","tid":284291,"uid":43407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T20:38:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E5%A1%B5%E7%BF%BC%E7%9E%AC%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AFk%E6%88%BF-1858365591112043/?fref=ts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E5%25A1%25B5%25E7%25BF%25BC%25E7%259E%25AC%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%258C%25AFk%25E6%2588%25BF-1858365591112043%2F%3Ffref%3Dts&d=7zzUWbBCWXR1ISRxLjE2bIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=10e3f9d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E5%A1%B5%E7%BF%BC%E7%9E%AC%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AFk%E6%88%BF-1858365591112043/?fref=ts</a><br />\n<br />\n各位有興趣可以去小弟個Facebook page參觀下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3859c13e4c664389bfc29e9e80de3278a6f01b61","tid":284291,"uid":117664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T00:18:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主用邊間玩?</blockquote><br />\nICMarket</blockquote><br />\n我覺得icmarket 個spread 好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6034c5e4797908e5625c86f927e48e56f2705f5a","tid":284291,"uid":81340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T00:20:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主用邊間玩?</blockquote><br />\nICMarket</blockquote><br />\n我覺得icmarket 個spread 好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n邊間平?"},{"pid":"79c675047376abaf146017c6907007784d312d01","tid":284291,"uid":117664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T00:20:48.000Z","msg":"有冇寫番個ea自動買賣<img src=\"/assets